notes: usman Ghani: 50 runs off 74 balls in 89 minutes, 5x4 1x6
Drinks: Afghanistan: 143 runs/4wkts, after 35 overs,10ex,13x4 1x6, (Usman G 77, Mohammad N. 5)
Usmani Ghani: 100 runs off 125 balls,in 178 minutes 10x4 1x6
1st wicket:54 runs off 51 balls,38 minutes,5ex,6x4 2x6 (Masakadza H, 22, Raza 27)
1st wicket: 100 runs off 103 balls in 69 minutes,5 ex, 9x4 3x6, (H.Masakadza 46, Raza 49)
1st wicket:152 runs off 148 bals, in 99 minutes, 7ex, 13x4 7x6 (H.Masakadza 56, Raza S.89)
S.Raza: 101 runs off 95 balls, in 119 minutes, 7x4 6x6
1st Wicket: 200 runs off 193 balls, in 125 minutes,8ex, 17x4 7x6,(H.Masakadza 83, S.Raza 109)

milestones.description: Masakadza and Sikandar Raza's 224-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 167 between Masakadza and Vusi Sibanda
Mohammad Nabi has become the top scorer for AFG in ODIs with 887 runs, going past Shahzad's 884
This is the highest match aggregate (513) involving teams Zimbabwe & Afghanistan in ODIs
Masakadza and Sikandar Raza's 224-run partnership is ZIM's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 202 between Sean Ervine and Carlisle
Samiullah Shinwari has scored 7 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for AFG breaking Mohammad Nabi's record
Dawlat Zadran has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for AFG, going past Shapoor's 3
Mohammad Nabi has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (35) for AFG, going past Samiullah Shinwari
